            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股今半日市。恒生指數開跌65點或0.25%，報26501，恒生科技指數開跌10點或0.19%，報5350點 ; 恒生國企指數開跌7點或0.08%，報9025點，大市成交27.38億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20240530_fi_aia_01299_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20240530_fi_aia_01299_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">友邦(01299)升0.87%，報81元，成交居首。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988)跌1.8%，報152.6元; 騰訊(00700)跌0.38%，報530元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金沙中國(01928)跌0.22%，報18.46元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">雲白國際(00030)飆11.77%，報0.285元，於9:01am錄得市前大手交易 ; 5100藏冰川(01115)升3.23%，報0.64%，上午09:04出現大手賣出，成交量為2.32千萬，成交價為0.6</p>\n</div>",
