            "title": "北海康城向藥明折讓近15%配股  集資近2億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">北海康成(01228)擬向藥明生物(02269)配股，每股配售價2.38元，較上周五收市價2.79元折讓14.7%；涉資項1.99億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"北海康成官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/01228-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"北海康成官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/01228-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">北海康成官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司向間接全資附屬公司WuXi Biologics HealthCare Venture配售8403.36萬股新股，佔擴大後股本約14.12%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司計劃把所得款項淨額約1.99億元，用於商業化產品的營運資金及註冊維護、現有產品線的研發開支，及結算集團的貿易應付款項。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">緊隨交割後，WuXi Biologics HealthCare Venture持股2.51%增至16.27%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15666048-%e5%8c%97%e6%b5%b7%e5%ba%b7%e5%9f%8e%e5%90%91%e8%97%a5%e6%98%8e%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%93%e8%bf%9115%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1-%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%87%e8%bf%912%e5%84%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/01228.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 09:20:47",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "金沙中國上年度經調整物業EBITDA按年減0.7%  末期息0.5元增1倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金沙中國(01928)公布，集團於截至2025年12月31日止年度的經調整物業EBITDA為23.1億美元（179.9億元），較截至2025年12月31日止年度的23.3億美元（180.9億元）減少0.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">派末期息0.5元，按年增加1倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：金沙中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20240909_FI_source-web_01928_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：金沙中國官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20240909_FI_source-web_01928_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：金沙中國官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至2025年12月31日止年度的利潤為 8.96億美元（69.7億元），較截至2024年12月331日止年度的10.5億美元（81.2億元）減少14.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至2025年12月31日止年度的淨收益總額為74.4億美元（579.1億元），較截至2024年12月31日止年度的70.8億美元（549.9億元）增加5.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15666009-%e9%87%91%e6%b2%99%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%b8%8a%e5%b9%b4%e5%ba%a6%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e7%89%a9%e6%a5%adebitda%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e6%b8%9b0-7-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af0-5%e5%85%83%e5%a2%9e1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240909_FI_source-web_sands_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 09:20:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國白銀折讓近18%配股",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國白銀集團(00815)配股集資，配股價0.51元，較2月13日收市價折讓17.74%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/775x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_00815_WEB.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/775x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_00815_WEB.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司年報</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">配售股份數量相當於經配發擴大後已發行股本的約23.06%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">認購所得款項總額將約為4.64億元，淨額將約為4.63億元，所得款項淨額的約40%用作於日喀則礦的20%股權的預期資本開支出資，用於在日喀則礦進行普查及其他勘探作業、所得款項淨額的約40%預留作向西藏日喀則提供進一步融資之用。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15665997-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%99%bd%e9%8a%80%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%93%e8%bf%9118%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_00815_WEB_1_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 09:00:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期跌25點   ADR低水72點   阿里滙控推低恒指",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期跌25點或0.09%，報26515。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指周五收市低水72點或0.27%，報26494點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230823_FI_source-web_02269-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230823_FI_source-web_02269-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藥明生物官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">藥明生物(02269) ADR折合港元計收報41.24元，較香港收市價高3.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690) ADR折合港元計收報83.65元，較香港收市價高1.8%; 網易(09999) ADR折合港元計收報188.26元，較香港收市價高1.4% ; 攜程(09961) ADR折合港元計收報188.26元，較香港收市價高1.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988) ADR折合港元計收報152.19元，較香港收市價低2.1% ，影響恒指43點 ; 騰訊(00700) ADR折合港元計收報533.81元，較香港收市價低0.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報133.14元，較香港收市價低1.9%，影響恒指48點 ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣80.1元，較香港收市價低水0.3% ; 港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣404.5元，較香港收市價低0.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">比亞迪(01211) ADR折合港元計收報95.85元，較香港收市價低1.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指夜市期指收報26560點，升30點，較昨日恒指收市26567點，低水7點，成交29943張。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國指夜市期指收報9051點，較昨日國指收市高水18點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15665980-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c25%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b472%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e6%8e%a8%e4%bd%8e%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 08:46:25",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
