            "title": "巴士的專題｜備戰春節檔 百度、騰訊、阿里、字節豪擲45億搶攻AI市場",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">春節臨近，各家AI巨頭紛紛加碼，百度文心助手、騰訊元寶、阿里千問、字節豆包等已經豪擲共超45億元，但是否能留住用戶還有待觀察。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其中，騰訊元寶App派10億元(人民幣‧下同)現金紅包，百度以5億元紅包綁定文心助手AI特效與集卡玩法，阿里千問App推出30億元「請客計劃」，字節跳動豆包則在春晚期間送出10萬份科技好禮以及最高8888元新春現金紅包，各家投入真金白銀，培養用戶使用AI的習慣。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"百度以5億元紅包綁定文心助手AI特效與集卡玩法。百度微信公眾號圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-2-1024x576.jpeg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"百度以5億元紅包綁定文心助手AI特效與集卡玩法。百度微信公眾號圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-2-1024x576.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">百度以5億元紅包綁定文心助手AI特效與集卡玩法。百度微信公眾號圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"字節跳動豆包送出10萬份科技好禮以及最高8888元新春現金紅包。豆包微信公眾號圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1152x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-3.jpeg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"字節跳動豆包送出10萬份科技好禮以及最高8888元新春現金紅包。豆包微信公眾號圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1152x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-3.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">字節跳動豆包送出10萬份科技好禮以及最高8888元新春現金紅包。豆包微信公眾號圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"阿里千問App推出30億元「請客計劃」。千問微信公眾號圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-4.jpeg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"阿里千問App推出30億元「請客計劃」。千問微信公眾號圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-4.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">阿里千問App推出30億元「請客計劃」。千問微信公眾號圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"騰訊元寶App派10億元現金紅包。元寶微信公眾號圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1060x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-1.jpeg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"騰訊元寶App派10億元現金紅包。元寶微信公眾號圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1060x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-1.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">騰訊元寶App派10億元現金紅包。元寶微信公眾號圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"百度以5億元紅包綁定文心助手AI特效與集卡玩法。百度微信公眾號圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-2-1024x576.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">百度以5億元紅包綁定文心助手AI特效與集卡玩法。百度微信公眾號圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"字節跳動豆包送出10萬份科技好禮以及最高8888元新春現金紅包。豆包微信公眾號圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1152x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-3.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">字節跳動豆包送出10萬份科技好禮以及最高8888元新春現金紅包。豆包微信公眾號圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"阿里千問App推出30億元「請客計劃」。千問微信公眾號圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-4.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">阿里千問App推出30億元「請客計劃」。千問微信公眾號圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"騰訊元寶App派10億元現金紅包。元寶微信公眾號圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1060x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-1.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">騰訊元寶App派10億元現金紅包。元寶微信公眾號圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"百度以5億元紅包綁定文心助手AI特效與集卡玩法。百度微信公眾號圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-2-1024x576.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"百度以5億元紅包綁定文心助手AI特效與集卡玩法。百度微信公眾號圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-2-1024x576.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">百度以5億元紅包綁定文心助手AI特效與集卡玩法。百度微信公眾號圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">真正的AI大戰，在於誰能留住用戶，紅包大戰固然能吸引流量，但往往只能維持短暫熱度，搶完紅包後，能否留住用戶，仍要看是否能更高效解決實際問題，與其讓用戶學習AI複雜功能，不如讓AI直接幫做事。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"字節跳動豆包送出10萬份科技好禮以及最高8888元新春現金紅包。豆包微信公眾號圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1152x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-3.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"字節跳動豆包送出10萬份科技好禮以及最高8888元新春現金紅包。豆包微信公眾號圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1152x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-3.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">字節跳動豆包送出10萬份科技好禮以及最高8888元新春現金紅包。豆包微信公眾號圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>用戶使用千問共買1022噸雞蛋</strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">無論是阿里、騰訊還是百度，都在嘗試將自家AI嵌入實際的使用場景，其中阿里千問就嘗試將AI與紅包、訂外賣、買機票、網購等場景結合，據千問App透露，「春節30億大免單」活動上線6天，千問幫用戶完成下單1.2億筆，用戶共說了41億次「千問幫我」，而用戶使用免單卡購買的單品，除了奶茶，還有1022噸雞蛋。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"阿里千問App推出30億元「請客計劃」。千問微信公眾號圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-4.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"阿里千問App推出30億元「請客計劃」。千問微信公眾號圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-4.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">阿里千問App推出30億元「請客計劃」。千問微信公眾號圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">與此同時，AI大模型加速迭代更新，字節跳動連發三款模型：Seedance 2.0（視頻）、Seedream 5.0（圖像）及豆包2.0；阿里巴巴則預告發布Qwen 3.5；智譜於2月11日正式推出GLM-5（代號Pony Alpha），參數翻倍至7440億，號稱在Agent能力上達開源SOTA水平。DeepSeek也將發布V4版本，改進編程能力及超長提示詞處理；MiniMax則於同日在Agent平台上線最新大模型M2.5。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"騰訊元寶App派10億元現金紅包。元寶微信公眾號圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1060x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-1.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"騰訊元寶App派10億元現金紅包。元寶微信公眾號圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1060x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_AI-1.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">騰訊元寶App派10億元現金紅包。元寶微信公眾號圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">但參數與技術指標在春節的場景並不佔優勢。DeepSeek編程能力再強也難以被感知；反倒是「幫我買奶茶」這種即時可見的能力，更容易在短期內留下深刻印象。因此今年的AI產品競爭，誰可以被用戶快速接受，就有望在今年的春節檔脫穎而出。</p>\n</div>",
